# User Story Template

## Title:
*As a [type of user], I want [an action] so that [a benefit/a goal].*

## Description:
- **What** is the user story? Describe what is being requested.
- **Why** is this important? Describe the business or user value.

## Acceptance Criteria:
- [ ] Given that [context or pre-condition], when [action], then [expected result].
- [ ] Include all relevant conditions and edge cases.

## Priority:
- [ ] High
- [ ] Medium
- [ ] Low

## Story Points/Estimate:
- [Estimate the effort or time needed]

## Dependencies:
- Any related stories, features, or systems.

## Additional Notes:
- Any relevant details, clarifications, or considerations.
